  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of AFQ056 in Reducing L-dopa Induced Dyskinesias in Parkinson's Disease Patients, and Safety in Combination With L-dopa</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-centre, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled, Parallel-group, Multiple Oral Dose Titration Study in Patients With Parkinson's Disease to Assess the Efficacy of AFQ056 in Reducing L-dopa Induced Dyskinesias, and the Safety and Tolerability of AFQ056 in Combination With L-dopa</official_title>
  <sponsors>
