  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety and efficacy of administration of AFQ056 in combination
      with L-dopa, in reducing the number of L-dopa related dyskinesias in Parkinson's disease
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
